          Standard Protocol
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          A universal language that lets any AI tool talk to any application,
          just like how websites use HTTP.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Real-time Access -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div
          class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-purple-500 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 flex items-center justify-center">
